subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Justine Henin rallied to defeat Nicole Vaidisova, 3-6, 6-3, 7-5, to advance to the final of the Zurich Open today against Tatiana Golovin, who defeated Francesca Schiavone, 6-0, 6-4.
